{"title":"UTalca. Aplasia medular","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Hematología/UTalca. Aplasia medular-2025-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Aplasia\\Nmedular","guid":"yFZ9Ys68IGG4VWMwi4_UKw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"## 1. INTRODUCCIÓN","guid":"u4g6LObxU_QJcaXRu4o-zA","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"- Falla medular caracterizada por disminución variable en recuentos periféricos sanguíneos","guid":"b4vp0nDZXwpzROtVugw33Q","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"- Origen en reducción de producción efectiva en médula ósea","guid":"2W9zFqnKp1o__3KE9D3n_g","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"- Puede afectar una serie específica (monocitopenia) o todas (pancitopenia)","guid":"z9YXLJ2ue33FtvP0tMvK_Q","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"- Primer caso descrito en 1888 por Paul Ehrlich","guid":"7Z-CTyrbJ3QqnnKaQoWKIA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"- Enfermedad originada por lesión de células hematopoyéticas pluripotenciales","guid":"-dsPHFCyVIqLUhQAszLvfg","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"1","text":"- Presentación subaguda con pancitopenia en sangre periférica","guid":"CnAfmaNWiN4xgZrhK9yxBQ","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"1","text":"- Diagnóstico obligatorio mediante biopsia médula ósea","guid":"Q0xhtwTufgv2E8oKjgvxaQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"- Causas adquiridas, hereditarias o congénitas","guid":"88IbDHVlKlnmPtAjC7sYCQ","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"- Curso clínico variable","guid":"QWvwgnGAvogbBH5PsTl2hQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"# CLASIFICACIÓN DE SEVERIDAD\\NEN APLASIA MEDULAR","guid":"88wbys1UxDF9QEpeiZ27KQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"## Aplasia medular severa\\N(Camita et al, 1976)","guid":"chQw7yDHvMb24qRVw4sF5g","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"- Médula ósea","guid":"oxIGJBA84f7ovN8habrQBQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"- Celularidad menor al 25% ó","guid":"-wiNmc5YVWIuq_dM1__GlA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"- 25-50% con menos de 30% células hematopoyéticas","guid":"unJZrX6bJ-F4yZU5utRkUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"- Sangre periférica\\N(dos de los 3 criterios)","guid":"8eFYPSFxNh5OUMmbAwvQhA","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"- Neutrófilos menores de 500","guid":"C0x_NczCVKtxbRSJ9Qdcqg","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"- Plaquetas menores 20.000","guid":"gHXDIzos3_9DTkbV03jjsg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"- Reticulocitos menores a 1%","guid":"nUQ1OBrlt0-zSCcQwyDUkA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"11","text":"## Aplasia medular muy severa\\N(Bacigalupo et al, 1988)","guid":"4pKa03RSr7-zLvkraq12aw","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"- Neutrófilos menores de 200","guid":"BB46yfthccX3xrxbTNJvHg","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"11","text":"## Hipoplasia o aplasia leve","guid":"QKYR3Vnuy-8QM214Xag8mQ","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"- Paciente con pancitopenia que no cumple requisitos anteriores","guid":"UnECGjO_Q0S9AuV697p-Mw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"# EXÁMENES DIAGNÓSTICOS\\NPARA APLASIA MEDULAR","guid":"UV2Lky4L0xwYvAG1wa0xRw","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"## Laboratorio de\\NHematología","guid":"SJVLr5ExvrPVQJDT3SGm1A","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"- Hemograma, recuento de reticulocitos, frotis sanguíneo, hemoglobina fetal","guid":"Gqs5cfkR3ePwxaARf0nCKA","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"- Coagulación: estudio completo (Actividad de Protrombina, Tiempo de Tromboplastina Parcial, Fibrinógeno, Dímero D)","guid":"Ah59F1RwwsMWv1Q34H78bA","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"- Perfil de hierro (ferritina, ferremia, transferrina, índice de saturación de transferrina)","guid":"GL0G8HKWzmnLVJ_qPgkSgw","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"25","text":"- Citometría de flujo: estudio