tías","guid":"04EUyRRihZC6QcSKUPN7mg","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"41","text":"- Ampliación según historia clínica","guid":"0ZrlV5SlW4dCW-uvZplOnQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"24","text":"## Pruebas de imagen","guid":"bTW9LQSzIi-h3WxyqaDk5Q","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"- Radiografía de tórax","guid":"9wwTJu520Yf4NZ8v_leEKA","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"- Radiografía de huesos largos y cráneo","guid":"QocZq64-NC-GIfSN6UM95A","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"46","text":"- Ecografía abdominal","guid":"ttIEPpWQnP5GYhuzW2gSvA","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"46","text":"- Otras según clínica","guid":"C8J9GT40e-yPtC_561-LZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"51","parent":"24","text":"## Tipificación de antígenos\\Nleucocitarios humanos (HLA)","guid":"3x_MlcxNw_fggpfhbKtXyQ","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"- Estudio HLA del paciente y familiares de primer grado","guid":"S9I51H2Z6sUi9MOJXCEEUw","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"- Realizar lo antes posible tras diagnóstico para posible trasplante precoz","guid":"moKwS2tZmGMRyJ0POP6mZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"24","text":"## Estudio de la\\Nmédula ósea","guid":"d_jot_w-U6xdg-FiHgiUGw","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"- Mielograma","guid":"P3VI5uV7ehKBVR-nZn-opQ","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"- Biopsia médula ósea","guid":"Dk-jLfOfOU_mhtWW4uvLeQ","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"- Cariograma de médula ósea","guid":"o2D9VDs3o-XVGiRyCv3xyQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"24","text":"## Estudio\\Ngenético","guid":"vPwkrntpiHaQgDLjH5-mwg","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"- Estudios moleculares mediante secuenciación masiva","guid":"7dRjm-qeoQf_GgnYua7OYA","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"- Diagnóstico específico de síndromes asociados a insuficiencias medulares","guid":"3ilnQ7XK079gJ_kYz6erVA","children":[]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"24","text":"## Estudio de fragilidad\\Ncromosómica","guid":"_YrYXKiIEcX4im9bOjieVQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"- Screening diagnóstico en todo paciente menor de 50 años","guid":"ZFIITKBk_VKc_1QWxAP0SQ","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"- Recomendado antes de trasplante alogénico en donante familiar","guid":"P4VSlBJ46wDj9pxVGqi7CQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"0","text":"## 2. APLASIA\\NMEDULAR ADQUIRIDA","guid":"L7sMBq8eCI2UXeHnOzWASQ","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"- Forma más frecuente","guid":"oRYf7_qkPodBznq-t0i18g","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"- 75% sin etiología determinable (posible mecanismo autoinmune)","guid":"44foOPj1IF-LGChVUAU6Dw","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"64","text":"- Causas identificables: fármacos, agentes químicos, hepatitis viral, enfermedades inmunes","guid":"AW2OMoJfuJzImVlUM--fOQ","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"64","text":"### 2.1. Epidemiología","guid":"UxSD81_GaCQXMcrDrc1GJg","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"- Distribución geográfica característica\\N(patrón opuesto a leucemia)","guid":"2ge-FUREgZALhKh2VDYo4A","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"- Mayor incidencia en países del tercer mundo","guid":"PKLACPSLYuzfeqq2uraY2g","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"- Países desarrollados: 2 casos/millón","guid":"wxuSj0RM1Ym63egowKnx-g","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"69","text":"- Regiones rurales de Tailandia: hasta 6 casos/millón","guid":"iym2t8bRlN-g2mnT705S2A","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"69","text":"- Ciudad de México: 3,9 casos/millón","guid":"vpeDxw7og9AdA6tKJ20h5g","children":[]}]},{"id":"74","parent":"68","text":"- Rango etario: 10-25 años y después de 60 años","guid":"i1aghD4xrixVYSQ5LdMk9A","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"68","text":"- Afecta por igual a ambos sexos","guid":"Grp7UeZcE1OSUH9eqp6vow","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"68","text":"- Mortalidad uniforme hasta 55 años, incremento sustancial después","guid":"4I-vS6_JSnNZSmlQhrBbTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"64","text":"### 2.2. Cuadro clínico","guid":"Wu-RnBt7wvYndicXy4muyg","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"- Síntomas de anemia","guid":"VOwaOwm-f_fsjAfZ_mOeAg","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"- Hemorragias de piel y mucosas","guid":"wfrXa98c05eCOCuAB3fDjQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"- Alteraciones visuales (hemorragias intrarretinales)","guid":"4dVfT5BzIOtMfQ8cxJ3v6A","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"77","text":"- Neutropenia: úlceras bucales, infecciones bacterianas, fiebre","guid":"84fsNqtOm3coFNOdIIAJSg","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"77","text":"- Manifestaciones varían según velocidad de instalación y vida media de elementos sanguíneos","guid":"qg58B_ApQdA0Eexr7AHC5Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"83","parent":"64","text":"### 2.3. Estudios\\Nde laboratorio","guid":"dZjiR8-ATKqasMgwdoIfNQ","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"- Característica principal: pancitopenia (puede ser precedida por una o dos citopenias)","guid":"vOVmZQMbw-kI4Znon5h9Ig","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"83","text":"#### 2.3.1.\\NSangre periférica","guid":"l3oAvKJ-IWGVrIooY9Hdeg","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"- Recuentos celulares uniformemente disminuidos","guid":"F2-wj6BLsMdncTcD0OoqGA","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"- Mayor compromiso de serie blanca y plaquetas","guid":"dJQXcELNkcUf_POeTMRdYQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"- Anemia normocítica/macrocítica y normocrómica","guid":"NL3yu6nQ5IKrSTNONrCvhQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"- RDW normal","guid":"lLCSjxaTmp4DlIWUlzuBTg","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"- Recuento reticulocitario disminuido","guid":"71mFQDtvh0lV_ht1qk4Tdg","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"- Plaquetas de tamaño normal","guid":"PANfn4w3JzjrI3Rii9fqUg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"85","text":"- Granulocitos disminuidos con función normal","guid":"pTyUNtN5STn0evHI3NLbcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"83","text":"#### 2.3.2. Otros estudios\\Nde laboratorio","guid":"IMhaj0LX8NBVh0nsNdsIdw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"- Posible incremento de hemoglobina fetal","guid":"HjWxyu1edBlmJ7w8Rzux8A","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"- Incremento de antígeno I en eritrocitos","guid":"mO6jv0hOP1hOhx-Ho_vMnQ","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"- Folato y vitamina B12 normales","guid":"MdNU5jvx-Wz3zdbhUZivlg","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"93","text":"- Eritropoyetina elevada","guid":"m8OBslIflGKzBlqVFlPunA","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"93","text":"- Hierro sérico normal o aumentado","guid":"RKcEPTunrZCPOHE56SzMcg","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"93","text":"- TIBC saturada","guid":"1L8O1dgOhDv7oYHN8l6Qew","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"93","text":"- Ferritina sérica elevada","guid":"5YJcdTz6exX7Rv09Z36FeQ","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"93","text":"- Estudios cromosómicos generalmente normales","guid":"vpHuowypakf68iRO6CHgHw","children":[]}]},{"id":"102","parent":"83","text":"#### 2.3.3. Médula ósea","guid":"JgjP86AkWdifHRk_RHA02A","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"- Imprescindible mielograma y biopsia médula ósea","guid":"6D-BlYTjZi-GpNdwuuLJRQ","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"- Cilindro de biopsia de al menos 2 cm de longitud","guid":"fgyq--oS-pPvG7eHSrWE-A","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"102","text":"- Hipocelularidad con espículas vacías y reemplazo por grasa","guid":"6ZMR41Uy4MOU1VryLegRbg","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"102","text":"- Predominio de linfocitos y células plasmáticas","guid":"Ucz-KYrepchIbUVtreQ9tQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"64","text":"# AGENTES ASOCIADOS A\\NAPLASIA MEDULAR","guid":"3QeqpVHLpNwiPLdNmGskIQ","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"## Fármacos","guid":"444ClApuPrJi7f774AzP1w","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"### Drogas que habitualmente\\Nproducen aplasia","guid":"Lyk341A4oFgYurLW0nFL2g","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"- Agentes quimioterápicos","guid":"FqYW-cNHMQ6eSJLqNfjwfg","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"109","text":"- Benceno","guid":"I-jf47CRN6xxiERpMxSOmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"### Reacciones\\Nidiosincráticas","guid":"J4mP-KNGS4aqlsMAlLPmnA","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"- Cloranfenicol","guid":"29Hwf8Yhuqy2YNgL0CX9TA","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"- Antiinflamatorios no esteroidales","guid":"aDj-EseK9MWxZAEclK7A2Q","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"- Sulfas","guid":"jxrNQrUVnPCmvOaVHXsTbw","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"- Antiepilépticos y sicotrópicos","guid":"Q5JjHCEbx5IRkdJgaiYLRw","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"112","text":"- Drogas antitiroídeas","guid":"jvUQ4F2iVL5N6EDDPPBuPw","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"112","text":"- Sales de oro","guid":"vwRs0x66evZQFcFQARZ6FA","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"112","text":"- Alopurinol","guid":"F6vQoh4VzIwgakybI0399w","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"112","text":"- Penicilamina","guid":"FbQZ3xZvdfxlm0BdSyaNlQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"121","parent":"107","text":"## Virus","guid":"LHDkv3mywxVX_wrvuEDSOQ","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"- Virus Ebstein Barr","guid":"Kx68EdCUwD3nmB9kRAufAg","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"- Virus Hepatitis A, No A, No B, No C, No G","guid":"b8UVjroBahaAuyqwi1Fdwg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"- VIH","guid":"8IrtAn5taD-qyqxLT7GXWg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"64","text":"### 2.4. Etiología","guid":"7C3TqjkOyrvPOxhMNhjWSA","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"- Mayoría catalogadas como \"idiopáticas\"","guid":"-7H5Wk1kh6aTI05QD6tlaQ","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"- Posible factor de huésped asociado (HLA-DR2)","guid":"GwVO0oOZKuSFpT2BXGGK6w","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"- Difícil establecer relación causa-efecto con medicamentos","guid":"XcElHSyvLNsPpYTOm_A_bQ","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"125","text":"- Pronóstico relacionado más con severidad que con agente causal","guid":"T4Ew8nQLSE6GHHhN-7XWhA","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"125","text":"- Clara relación causal con hepatitis viral","guid":"0lHzw_WxY0nsTQ-eEiYwiA","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"64","text":"### 2.5. Fisiopatología","guid":"tIvUomT3AoDzWpO91ABJkg","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"- Alteración numérica o funcional de células troncales hematopoyéticas","guid":"jnshbgECOMH9GruWTOWzhg","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"- Alteraciones en estroma de médula ósea","guid":"ceqqUzbGnfbB6dedAZGamw","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"- Combinación de ambas","guid":"fgDFQEHpsY64nTTk_BTDrg","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"131","text":"- Marcada disminución de células CD34+","guid":"pQWIoJFqi0jQAsadtw6nSQ","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"131","text":"- Pancitopenia cuando progenitores < 1% de valores normales","guid":"wmmxm16nT8tJrL89q5ChLg","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"131","text":"- Función celular normal en células estromales","guid":"ToXPAH8iSG6TV_-spp4agQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"131","text":"- Daño directo → Drogas citotóxicas, radioterapia, benceno","guid":"0HC4j8TQQUWE0a0g2aLS5w","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"131","text":"- Daño inmunológicamente mediado → Activación linfocitos T, producción IFNα, TNF, IL-2","guid":"rbLksmrIngZeg4HA1eZpgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"64","text":"### 2.6.\\NTratamiento y\\Nevolución","guid":"WucpJfhoKO6541tmVp2qig","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"- Objetivo: mejorar citopenias","guid":"wTLatw4TfCcTrU7H6vbUWw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"140","text":"- Opciones según severidad, causa y paciente","guid":"QMGQXqhpT33-WQiSvFoO_Q","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"140","text":"- Indicado para aplasia grave, muy grave o moderada con citopenia grave","guid":"I-Mz4vYITuHYlFWtaRpKYg","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"140","text":"# TRATAMIENTO DE SOPORTE\\NEN APLASIA MEDULAR","guid":"xQ7NKBY9XPH_rqcF2J1EWQ","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"## a) Nutrición","guid":"0pFPLZKTi9wAwweqS5Xz-w","children":[{"id":"146","parent":"145","text":"- Necesario aporte nutricional adecuado","guid":"McpYf4-1pJmjPhNax-cIxA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"145","text":"- Requerimientos basales incrementados (especialmente en infecciones)","guid":"AEVdyPHH2FMtMRs0YJZy6w","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"145","text":"- Deficiencia nutricional lleva rápidamente a desnutrición","guid":"3I1akkOLlaL_SO4g-MwC_g","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"145","text":"- En caso necesario, iniciar precozmente nutrición parenteral","guid":"Gh-_yoXtxfGb4ChAfsOcpg","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"144","text":"## b) Soporte\\Ntransfusional","guid":"m6p_lmRLhakH1QtDjYeXHg","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"- Apoyo con plaquetas y glóbulos rojos: importante avance en sobrevida","guid":"dVXFdz0cKrrWFzwNC4JW4g","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"- Ha cambiado causa principal de muerte de hemorragia a infección","guid":"YaTCV7LBW3VER8KVisuwVA","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"- Objetivos principales:","guid":"4U9yZXGX7F0OXfF3KWe_iA","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"- Disminuir riesgo de secuelas por accidentes hemorrágicos","guid":"BNcE6rCYDJrDqcVikjgFCw","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"153","text":"- Evitar alosensibilización","guid":"OsNCzQA9DkAXxcbi02FAEw","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"- Reducir riesgo de enfermedades transmisibles","guid":"Ar-ACh-qiXOOMTFSGv2EJQ","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"153","text":"- Productos deben ser idealmente filtrados e irradiados","guid":"_YoBtT7TTAq2HvcIR_S0_g","children":[]}]},{"id":"158","parent":"150","text":"### Hemorragia","guid":"cF3rBiqX8yMhCpmkudws4w","children":[{"id":"159","parent":"158","text":"- Transfundir plaquetas si:","guid":"AZGZ8hke9Xlns6qsB0IwAg","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"- Recuento ≤10.000/μL","guid":"8l7ywRau5ejHg81823Qg4w","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"- Presencia de sangrado","guid":"ohJqWsPPb0olvbb2RmqIFg","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"- Cuadro febril no controlado","guid":"p8-u9jSvs6dtD_awMgvGmw","children":[]}]},{"id":"163","parent":"158","text":"- Preferencia: plaquetas de\\Naféresis de donante único","guid":"D6cjyOtZtvyK4Fpbyi99vg","children":[{"id":"164","parent":"163","text":"- Disminuye riesgo de aloinmunización","guid":"XrR4WJ5lz5SOkycze8HiKg","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"163","text":"- Reduce refractariedad a transfusión de plaquetas","guid":"78kBoJsO8JsedjFrzsUcqQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"158","text":"- Medidas\\Nadicionales:","guid":"cx5hyf-U8mPL6d3M_imTEw","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"- Buena higiene dental","guid":"ZxnIDdpSfi7iTgpT1Rljeg","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"- Cepillos suaves","guid":"Efl7dzKAxjIeL5K3-8xGUQ","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"- Evitar traumas (suspender deportes de riesgo)","guid":"-GQWRG4ZGhxuI44jPemzXA","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"- Compresión firme por 15 minutos tras extracción de sangre","guid":"T9DmmgGNJq7DRqPktvKEVA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"166","text":"- Tratamiento tópico y agentes antifibrinolíticos para sangrado local","guid":"Fz1L1x54_9tzGmB60V__pw","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"166","text":"- Evitar fármacos que interfieren con función plaquetaria (AAS, AINES)","guid":"wRUtJ00y5e-Le3vvCivSLg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"173","parent":"150","text":"### Anemia","guid":"3Gi0sm8K_ogPeOGE-j7EIQ","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"- Reposición con glóbulos rojos lavados o filtrados","guid":"UEWcrRfodZg1Z3sXrCzmpg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"- Remoción de leucocitos para evitar sensibilización","guid":"66MgU6tl688LV-RejOn8BQ","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"173","text":"- Valores de\\Nhemoglobina:","guid":"5PIHZiigvs7IX3iJegCM0A","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"- Inicialmente ~9 g/dL","guid":"BwbK8OjmeHMIEjOsFRJW4w","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"- Posteriormente manejo con valores hasta 6 g/dL (anemia crónica compensada)","guid":"4HeddAn00xjtf-gy18ugiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"179","parent":"173","text":"- Riesgo a largo plazo:\\Nsobrecarga de hierro","guid":"s39L3xe3OjQY00G3WG3YpA","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"- Puede dañar corazón, hígado y sistema endocrino","guid":"qckOph9MJxQNDjSYgImbGw","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"- Indicar quelantes de hierro antes del daño (~50 unidades transfundidas)","guid":"rXgupAZEhl_uGoChzbW7qA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"144","text":"## c) Infecciones","guid":"_Uiq_8PmNX6niIepmczpJQ","children":[{"id":"183","parent":"182","text":"- Principal causa de mortalidad en aplasia medular","guid":"Ff7G7qqRe60cbrdG-E8j1Q","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"182","text":"- Prevención y tratamiento tienen impacto en pronóstico","guid":"fGiykg7qc8Uy0iJJDFEr6Q","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"182","text":"- Necesidad de estudios de evaluación de profilaxis infecciosa","guid":"LjtVoK0smw6pkBuM-ynLJQ","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"182","text":"- Mayoría de recomendaciones adaptadas de otros contextos (enfermedades malignas, TPH)","guid":"oAkk7Jg6vxw2pned0g-mQw","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"182","text":"- Riesgo elevado de infecciones fúngicas por neutropenia profunda prolongada","guid":"Xpob2lJJqXw1lEKcrESHWg","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"182","text":"- Sin recomendaciones establecidas para iniciar profilaxis antifúngica según cifra de neutrófilos","guid":"INYShuLqb0WZ3RI535JdnQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"140","text":"# TRATAMIENTO Y RESPUESTA\\NEN APLASIA MEDULAR","guid":"IpLboxkanjr-wLQztLhSCA","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"## Objetivo principal","guid":"fWf7mRAYii09lcqONCVoWQ","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"- Restituir producción de series hematopoyéticas","guid":"Se3Mso8qaj6m7--ku6Tfeg","children":[]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"189","text":"## Líneas terapéuticas\\Nprincipales","guid":"OJ-pwveFUFqmAp442nduCg","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"1. Trasplante de progenitores hematopoyéticos (TPH)","guid":"56xI2e7uuKX_liYhy26t1g","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"192","text":"2. Inmunosupresión (linfoglobulina antitimocítica, ciclosporina, metilprednisolona)","guid":"pwvtLVnZXkceWN__dMi-og","children":[]}]},{"id":"195","parent":"189","text":"## Criterios de\\Nselección terapéutica","guid":"cVAnfFhhpEPXcLDbACiNLg","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"- Pacientes <20 años con donante familiar HLA idéntico:\\NTPH primera línea","guid":"bnrk_SMajNaSPayQXg_3Qg","children":[{"id":"197","parent":"196","text":"- Supervivencia global 80-90%","guid":"dTH7Dk4jXy835C5WMYby5w","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"196","text":"- Menor desarrollo EICH crónica","guid":"NmZ4OQLZtTDMIHqT_vdDMA","children":[]},{"id":"199","parent":"196","text":"- Bajo riesgo evolución clonal","guid":"k3HKQO6T6FhrvN78WnLujA","children":[]}]},{"id":"200","parent":"195","text":"- Donante no familiar HLA idéntico disponible:\\Nposible TPH primera línea","guid":"2qkkbZdVj1c7Uftw1_FSkw","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"- Basado en datos del Registro Europeo de Aplasia Medular (EBMT)","guid":"NQzueYBb-cjiMfGBG-BUQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"202","parent":"195","text":"- Pacientes >50 años: tratamiento\\Ninmunosupresor primera línea","guid":"IeaU_ZQFtQSU6UvqMzU5Kg","children":[{"id":"203","parent":"202","text":"- Supervivencia tras TPH ~50% a 10 años","guid":"vRkX6h8Jk5cdv9fScbkY9Q","children":[]},{"id":"204","parent":"202","text":"- Mayor riesgo fallo injerto y EICH","guid":"-0kHF0jvKEdfBsbgnL4ZQA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"205","parent":"189","text":"## a) Trasplante de progenitores\\Nhematopoyéticos","guid":"oVDKErAeul2uaAMyH-lJcg","children":[{"id":"206","parent":"205","text":"- Células obtenidas de donantes familiares HLA-A, HLA-B y HLA-DR compatibles","guid":"pD1KXqlyGQkXFvJWC3lysw","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"205","text":"- Acondicionamiento:\\Nciclofosfamida y Timoglobulina","guid":"eg-cianb9hBAoeICfYKWRQ","children":[{"id":"208","parent":"207","text":"- Elimina factor autoinmunidad","guid":"k5-iqhZVXQ8BveVt7kVRNg","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"207","text":"- Previene rechazo y EICH","guid":"Gz-kvkI8HxDp4GGx3n1YXQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"210","parent":"205","text":"- Recuperación medular: rápida, completa, estable","guid":"i3K2UpBCRXFgKL86Yad3fg","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"205","text":"- Tasas sobrevida:\\N75-80% (hasta 90%)","guid":"dkoTkDlRw6e2DrAippqOag","children":[{"id":"212","parent":"211","text":"- Sobrevida\\Nsegún edad:","guid":"BFQ5AGr-Ofmbsxt9AC-PtA","children":[{"id":"213","parent":"212","text":"- <20 años: 75%","guid":"AUemfNT0Onv2vk-7nnNWyg","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"212","text":"- 20-40 años: 68%","guid":"BMWQ9D5bMdB_-8BzR-7hzA","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"212","text":"- >40 años: 35%","guid":"zIrChXsH6JN952WcohUJdQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"216","parent":"205","text":"- Complicaciones\\Na largo plazo:","guid":"LHNwz9nftPjogEFepGOjPA","children":[{"id":"217","parent":"216","text":"- Enfermedad pulmonar restrictiva/obstructiva (25%)","guid":"eJtV9M2yh8jyJZiPwkjmlQ","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"216","text":"- Osteoporosis (18%)","guid":"_BhuZZHzl-9Xnrd15Cwp2w","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"216","text":"- Tumor sólido (12%)","guid":"fT2UQQsythVuKop_DfhDuQ","children":[]},{"id":"220","parent":"216","text":"- Mayor frecuencia si EICH","guid":"ryNtY2MuGJ1LRPsskM0cTA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"221","parent":"189","text":"## b) Tratamiento\\Ninmunosupresor","guid":"IAPbe7Z6C-z25fnEy41c7A","children":[{"id":"222","parent":"221","text":"- Indicaciones:","guid":"FxXShos9tA-cmsDb9FCRpA","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"- Aplasia grave/muy grave no candidatos a TPH","guid":"EmaRlS_SBSW1lCjYtTEFYw","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"- Aplasia moderada con necesidad transfusional/sangrados/infecciones limitantes","guid":"j7Ki6ymd47C4Gs-jTj7fIA","children":[]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"221","text":"- Globulina antilinfocítica (ALG)\\No antitimocítica (ATG):","guid":"N867bVTGAWqaXq2x_N6JCg","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"- Respuesta 40-70%","guid":"kS2BLGyyXwYqkQ_EiB4qNw","children":[]},{"id":"227","parent":"225","text":"- Actividad antilinfocítica directa como mecanismo principal","guid":"CvDu_QaDaxZsEm0nQXU60g","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"225","text":"- Reduce recuento linfocitos al 10% inicial","guid":"LKaDmDlSuDR_2IP3owHmUA","children":[]}]},{"id":"229","parent":"221","text":"- Tratamiento estándar actual:\\Nciclosporina + ATG","guid":"mFym18O2Wu_ONlP2Sl9YVQ","children":[{"id":"230","parent":"229","text":"- ATG de caballo superior a ATG de conejo","guid":"EG-l1xAIAIUsqCHf7frLKw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"231","parent":"189","text":"## c) Corticoides","guid":"-Ug6m2z_nqzJ36JohSmAGA","children":[{"id":"232","parent":"231","text":"- Inefectivo como agente único en dosis bajas","guid":"hnvjsdr_m3esEtM2xoTvTw","children":[]},{"id":"233","parent":"231","text":"- Metilprednisolona en dosis altas: efectiva pero alta toxicidad","guid":"NpEnkrSyeqOW0bwbzuDncw","children":[]},{"id":"234","parent":"231","text":"- Uso actual: periodos cortos, dosis moderada","guid":"m5jzJMdQHTiQT8ffG7atFg","children":[]},{"id":"235","parent":"231","text":"- Reduce efectos adversos ATG (anafilaxia, enfermedad del suero)","guid":"iIwzU4ed_cbxYWlZmtnSBA","children":[]}]},{"id":"236","parent":"189","text":"## d) Ciclofosfamida","guid":"nQ7PUufbxweencqnHMnCbw","children":[{"id":"237","parent":"236","text":"- Estudios iniciales (1980): dosis baja, sin respuesta","guid":"ZzNylhymck46wSvRQc9i1w","children":[]},{"id":"238","parent":"236","text":"- Estudios posteriores (2000): dosis alta, efectiva pero con complicaciones importantes","guid":"ASuFT3Z42iVYgbBNFsjhyQ","children":[]},{"id":"239","parent":"236","text":"- Uso actual: pacientes sin respuesta a otros esquemas","guid":"xwpMFH3--CIqijSvm11CSw","children":[]}]},{"id":"240","parent":"189","text":"## e) Anticuerpos\\Nmonoclonales","guid":"Fr7bohiRcAGccdqMntLCfA","children":[{"id":"241","parent":"240","text":"- Dirigidos contra antígenos de linfocitos T","guid":"d0QpAo0feYbg9dL_Y4Z0hw","children":[]},{"id":"242","parent":"240","text":"- Sin evidencia probada más allá de reportes anecdóticos","guid":"CG68bveLotAfNrR-JPC_VQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"243","parent":"189","text":"## f) Ciclosporina A (CsA)","guid":"VKdODmMdXfQrnSX9QwXRuQ","children":[{"id":"244","parent":"243","text":"- Potente inmunosupresor","guid":"xQ_fwWNJ8HTSSOmuBI896g","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"243","text":"- Inhibe transcripción genes IL2, INFγ, otras citoquinas","guid":"PFvCNp3BekidLaXrZbbItw","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"243","text":"- Bloqueo de etapas centrales respuesta inmune","guid":"wbfrkKy-oS44jaxadiF0vA","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"243","text":"- Eficacia comparable a ATG","guid":"7DnYfMG2Yt4A_IbdiHW2AQ","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"243","text":"- Efecto mayor en asociación con ATG","guid":"wimBewi9hNgJlj4TBhgdYw","children":[]}]},{"id":"249","parent":"189","text":"## g) Eltrombopag","guid":"IiysNowCKD2DcRBrwvuYeA","children":[{"id":"250","parent":"249","text":"- Interactúa con receptor de trombopoyetina (R-TPO)","guid":"iYH3iEZFBd0EUydhYqcuPg","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"249","text":"- Induce proliferación/diferenciación células progenitoras","guid":"erTl4YUvWHn501sLhfF6Jg","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"249","text":"- Útil en pacientes refractarios","guid":"cIhBmzX5uAq1nsUqpEOwgw","children":[]}]},{"id":"253","parent":"189","text":"## Respuesta al\\Ntratamiento","guid":"SiZImuM-ba6bbSZSFmL20g","children":[{"id":"254","parent":"253","text":"- Lenta (recuperación en 3 meses)","guid":"4z_QIaH6-QQLjSyJtXGKug","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"253","text":"- Si no hay respuesta: segundo ciclo con ATG (preferencia origen conejo)","guid":"qAf08W_mKuQRbz7zOiNPzw","children":[]}]},{"id":"256","parent":"189","text":"## Complicaciones\\Ntardías","guid":"abWaYOih3HXRgnJkan-EYA","children":[{"id":"257","parent":"256","text":"- Recaída (1/3 pacientes)","guid":"lqjCVasfjZD-NNpnMZe4ug","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"256","text":"- Dependencia a CsA (25%)","guid":"AmpSle4-kBNdycM4FEOeAg","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"256","text":"- Enfermedades hematológicas\\Nclonales (25%):","guid":"WXOLosrCQVuCX1l4BcXYEA","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"- Hemoglobinuria paroxística nocturna","guid":"FES32apjDdo6x3Fk4FUtFw","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"- Síndrome mielodisplásico","guid":"5qBwBu52zDQWaAoUHTt94Q","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"259","text":"- Leucemia mieloide aguda","guid":"mlz-eJFBHfOtID9PvguodA","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"259","text":"- Tumor sólido","guid":"aIcLe6mpl_YNbVQTsXvKOA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"264","parent":"189","text":"## Comparación TPH vs\\Ninmunosupresión","guid":"nfuROkThNTv-hj2cBsq3cw","children":[{"id":"265","parent":"264","text":"- Sobrevida a 5 años: equivalente en algunos estudios","guid":"Y-I1YiehBDOiSdzlZLuFdA","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"264","text":"- Desventajas inmunosupresión:","guid":"va2h5pqOpZ-EAE4a0pCMmQ","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"- Posibilidad recaída","guid":"Nmp7prBNN5U31MDhThyZLQ","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"- Respuesta hematológica incompleta","guid":"INf7rQT8I661W1tvy-IR5A","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"266","text":"- Efectos adversos (especialmente renales)","guid":"1XQ2BXPae4HqJlmeQ9ppeA","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"266","text":"- Dependencia a CsA (alto costo)","guid":"IK_JgCWAhtGXF-pfcBXG2Q","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"266","text":"- 25% enfermedad clonal/maligna","guid":"k5prN1byqaA3C63OZd3vlg","children":[]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"264","text":"- TPH: tratamiento de elección en <20 años","guid":"OTVWJFnP8nS53V0XOM9I4Q","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"273","parent":"64","text":"# HEMOGLOBINURIA\\NPAROXÍSTICA NOCTURNA","guid":"GVdFdspMwTjDXUHSC0U1EA","children":[{"id":"274","parent":"273","text":"- Trastorno adquirido clonal","guid":"acQCjKm8ftH2UzT0-1EcBQ","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"273","text":"- Célula madre hematopoyética y derivadas vulnerables al ataque del complemento","guid":"6RAX6ZD9QlwDi11fItjj6Q","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"273","text":"- Múltiples mutaciones somáticas identificadas en gen PIGA","guid":"n2mtrs-VOEIX_bL54Zu_zQ","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"273","text":"## Formas de\\Npresentación","guid":"Z2tfxSOOhGvPXdPZCbXQwA","children":[{"id":"278","parent":"277","text":"1. Típica: asociada a fenómeno hemolítico","guid":"6mLyr9PZazEZNXQ0XIcypw","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"277","text":"2. Relacionada con aplasia: clon HPN <10%","guid":"LH9mN6-8eHcb7heaZEjyqw","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"277","text":"3. Subclínica: clon HPN <1%","guid":"aJW7HmGpTnMpLjCQkHa6sQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"273","text":"## Relación con\\Naplasia medular","guid":"DxZqrueq-1-nlaYi1BskEg","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"- Pacientes con clon HPN\\Nasociado a aplasia:","guid":"sqgXe_8fs_G8nuahuaBoMA","children":[{"id":"283","parent":"282","text":"- Mayor probabilidad de respuesta al tratamiento inmunosupresor","guid":"OzQJEx8Za1V-exqcMeRE8A","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"282","text":"- Mejor pronóstico","guid":"As1H-tRlY10qVsJOEfWfhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"285","parent":"281","text":"- Desarrollo de clones HPN: efecto común y temprano en evolución de aplasia","guid":"ee-wdTMcntuoXf